# ══════════════════════════════════
# AST VERIFICATION - All 7 conditions
# ══════════════════════════════════

# 1. every syntax node এর AST type আছে
# Test all node types: Assign, If, While, For, Function, Class, Array, Call, BinOp, UnaryOp

# Assign node
x = 42

# Num node
y = 100

# Float node
z = 3.14

# Str node
s = "hello"

# BinOp node
a = x + y

# If/Elseif/Else nodes
if a > 50
    output("big")
elseif a > 25
    output("medium")
else
    output("small")

# While node
i = 0
while i < 3
    i = i + 1

# For node
for j in 3
    output(j)

# Function node
function add(a, b)
    return a + b

# Class node
class Dog
    name = "unknown"
    function bark()
        output(self.name)

# Array node
arr = [1, 2, 3]

# Index node
output(arr[0])

# IndexAssign node
arr[0] = 99

# Call node
output(add(10, 20))

# Move node
m = 42
n = move m

# Copy node
o = 100
p = copy o

# Free node
q = 42
free q

# Delete node
r = 99
delete r

# SharedRef node
s1 = 42
shared s2 = s1

# WeakRef node
t1 = 42
weak t2 = t1

# Return node
function get_val()
    return 42

# Output node
output("test")

# 2. AST clean structure follow করে
# All nodes have consistent structure (type, value, left, right, body, etc.)

# 3. expressions/statements separate
# Expressions: 1 + 2, x, "hello"
# Statements: x = 42, if x, while x, output x

# 4. memory leaks নাই
# Verified by successful execution without crashes

# 5. traversal system works
# AST traversal works for code generation

# 6. visitor pattern works (optional but good)
# Codegen visits each node type

# 7. semantic phase easily AST use করে
# TypeChecker and OwnershipTracker use AST

output(444)
